  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Warning: The game might be scary and has a rather WTF sense of humor!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>If you enjoy experiencing something unique and strange, you're going to love it!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game can control your mouse to scare you — moving game windows and more...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(Also, if you’re a streamer, make sure to record using <strong>screen capture</strong> so everything is visible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Also, there’s no nudity unless you explicitly write it in.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/8912509b1bfe9b70bea6a14a2a541e05.avif?t=1768883392\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras_big/8912509b1bfe9b70bea6a14a2a541e05.webp?t=1768883392 width=1560 height=941 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[Game Quality]:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Many free updates to come!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/2ce1f6f1a0b71a5f3a7b19cdec9be835.poster.avif?t=1768883392\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/2ce1f6f1a0b71a5f3a7b19cdec9be835.webm?t=1768883392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/2ce1f6f1a0b71a5f3a7b19cdec9be835.mp4?t=1768883392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Horror with choices impacting the story. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/cb27ddaa0d95f88106982886273e265e.poster.avif?t=1768883392\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/cb27ddaa0d95f88106982886273e265e.webm?t=1768883392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/cb27ddaa0d95f88106982886273e265e.mp4?t=1768883392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- References to anime, games, memes, and real events. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Gameplay transitions from 2D to 3D. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Varied attacks, from melee to explosive bombs!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/d0c24a5d41af5c929cb6b3deb8e41972.poster.avif?t=1768883392\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/d0c24a5d41af5c929cb6b3deb8e41972.webm?t=1768883392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/d0c24a5d41af5c929cb6b3deb8e41972.mp4?t=1768883392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Farming to become powerful and fast!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/b26d20c510316bbd772dfdb3aeb5e815.poster.avif?t=1768883392\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/b26d20c510316bbd772dfdb3aeb5e815.webm?t=1768883392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/b26d20c510316bbd772dfdb3aeb5e815.mp4?t=1768883392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Boss battles with their own stories. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Elaborate story, filled with secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/ad5451933c5d7803cb6f924a9ebe3e27.poster.avif?t=1768883392\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/ad5451933c5d7803cb6f924a9ebe3e27.webm?t=1768883392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/ad5451933c5d7803cb6f924a9ebe3e27.mp4?t=1768883392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Replayability.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Playable for up to 3 players! You can even go through the main story in cooperation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/6274b86d9910853b8bc5c9445b1a927d.avif?t=1768883392\" width=600 height=308 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Addresses current sensitive topics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Jet board and stunts! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/603b8d2ab1633d2a4c9799254dc2801f.poster.avif?t=1768883392\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/603b8d2ab1633d2a4c9799254dc2801f.webm?t=1768883392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/603b8d2ab1633d2a4c9799254dc2801f.mp4?t=1768883392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Video games! Yes, you can play games within this game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/6959f0580799a3f65d65e017a14dec13.poster.avif?t=1768883392\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/6959f0580799a3f65d65e017a14dec13.webm?t=1768883392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/6959f0580799a3f65d65e017a14dec13.mp4?t=1768883392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Pull-ups to boost life! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Flirting through your choices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Relationship and gift shop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Shop to buy cool things!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Casino for betting XP.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Quick Time Events (QTE) battles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >--------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/d7b4961e5ea6949653ffb084a66933f3.poster.avif?t=1768883392\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/d7b4961e5ea6949653ffb084a66933f3.webm?t=1768883392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/d7b4961e5ea6949653ffb084a66933f3.mp4?t=1768883392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >--------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And even more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Oh yes, and one of the most incredible things is</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Moyori Kimina.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/a985fd08180efa2c5d6007de1b011693.avif?t=1768883392\" width=500 height=579 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Age: Over 13.8 billion years</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She is the universe of Résop Paz.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And she is in love with you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are her favorite player.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is mainly available in <strong>French</strong> and <strong>English</strong>, which are the two primary languages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It also offers <strong>18 additional alternative languages</strong>, translated in an <strong>approximate</strong> way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👉 These 18 secondary languages <strong>do not include special characters</strong>, and some parts may not yet be fully translated, but they allow players to <strong>play the game without blocking issues</strong>.<br>👉 The <strong>main story remains playable and translated</strong> in these alternative languages.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>List of available alternative languages (approximate translations):</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>es</strong> — Spanish (Español)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>pt</strong> — Brazilian Portuguese (Português – Brasil)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>de</strong> — German (Deutsch)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>pl</strong> — Polish (Polski)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>tr</strong> — Turkish (Türkçe)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>it</strong> — Italian (Italiano)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>cz</strong> — Czech (Čeština)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>hu</strong> — Hungarian (Magyar)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>nl</strong> — Dutch (Nederlands)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>sv</strong> — Swedish (Svenska)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>da</strong> — Danish (Dansk)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>fi</strong> — Finnish (Suomi)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ro</strong> — Romanian (Română)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>vb</strong> — Flemish (Vlaams)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>no</strong> — Norwegian (Bokmål)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>id</strong> — Indonesian (Bahasa Indonesia)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ch</strong> — Swiss German (Schweizerdeutsch)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ie</strong> — Irish (Irish English)</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Warning: The game might be scary and has a rather WTF sense of humor!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>If you enjoy experiencing something unique and strange, you're going to love it!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game can control your mouse to scare you — moving game windows and more...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(Also, if you’re a streamer, make sure to record using <strong>screen capture</strong> so everything is visible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Also, there’s no nudity unless you explicitly write it in.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/8912509b1bfe9b70bea6a14a2a541e05.avif?t=1768883392\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras_big/8912509b1bfe9b70bea6a14a2a541e05.webp?t=1768883392 width=1560 height=941 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[Game Quality]:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Many free updates to come!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/2ce1f6f1a0b71a5f3a7b19cdec9be835.poster.avif?t=1768883392\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/2ce1f6f1a0b71a5f3a7b19cdec9be835.webm?t=1768883392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/2ce1f6f1a0b71a5f3a7b19cdec9be835.mp4?t=1768883392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Horror with choices impacting the story. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/cb27ddaa0d95f88106982886273e265e.poster.avif?t=1768883392\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/cb27ddaa0d95f88106982886273e265e.webm?t=1768883392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/cb27ddaa0d95f88106982886273e265e.mp4?t=1768883392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- References to anime, games, memes, and real events. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Gameplay transitions from 2D to 3D. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Varied attacks, from melee to explosive bombs!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/d0c24a5d41af5c929cb6b3deb8e41972.poster.avif?t=1768883392\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/d0c24a5d41af5c929cb6b3deb8e41972.webm?t=1768883392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/d0c24a5d41af5c929cb6b3deb8e41972.mp4?t=1768883392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Farming to become powerful and fast!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/b26d20c510316bbd772dfdb3aeb5e815.poster.avif?t=1768883392\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/b26d20c510316bbd772dfdb3aeb5e815.webm?t=1768883392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/b26d20c510316bbd772dfdb3aeb5e815.mp4?t=1768883392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Boss battles with their own stories. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Elaborate story, filled with secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/ad5451933c5d7803cb6f924a9ebe3e27.poster.avif?t=1768883392\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/ad5451933c5d7803cb6f924a9ebe3e27.webm?t=1768883392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/ad5451933c5d7803cb6f924a9ebe3e27.mp4?t=1768883392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Replayability.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Playable for up to 3 players! You can even go through the main story in cooperation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/6274b86d9910853b8bc5c9445b1a927d.avif?t=1768883392\" width=600 height=308 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Addresses current sensitive topics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Jet board and stunts! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/603b8d2ab1633d2a4c9799254dc2801f.poster.avif?t=1768883392\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768440/extras/603b8d2ab1633d2a4c9799254dc2801f.webm?t=1768883392\" type=\"video/webm; codec